ActDirector of Public Prosecutions Act
PrecisAuthorization of GEORGE G. DOLHAI of Ottawa, Ontario, Deputy Director of Public Prosecutions, to act as Director of Public Prosecutions, during pleasure, to fill a vacancy in that office for a term ending March 5, 2017, or until a Director of Public Prosecutions is appointed, whichever occurs first.
